    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Ranger Trap</strong><br/><br/><p><b>Effect </b>A ranger can only add this to a fire trap. If the triggering creature fails its Reflex save, it catches on fire, taking 1d6 points of fire damage at the start of its turn for 1d4 rounds. The burning creature can attempt a new save as a full-round action. Dropping and rolling on the ground grants a +4 bonus on this save.</p>",
